    <item>
      <title>Install the Google Chrome Web Browser on Ubuntu Linux</title>
      <link>https://www.vandenboom.icu/en/blog/2022-installeer-de-google-chrome-web-browser-op-ubuntu-linux/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Apr 2022 11:51:54 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://www.vandenboom.icu/en/blog/2022-installeer-de-google-chrome-web-browser-op-ubuntu-linux/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;$ wget -q -O - &lt;a href=&#34;https://dl.google.com/linux/linux_signing_key.pub&#34;&gt;https://dl.google.com/linux/linux_signing_key.pub&lt;/a&gt; | sudo apt-key add -&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;$ sudo sh -c &amp;rsquo;echo &amp;ldquo;deb [arch=amd64] &lt;a href=&#34;http://dl.google.com/linux/chrome/deb/&#34;&gt;http://dl.google.com/linux/chrome/deb/&lt;/a&gt; stable main&amp;rdquo; &amp;raquo; /etc/apt/sources.list.d/google-chrome.list&#39;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;$ sudo apt update&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;$ sudo apt install google-chrome-stable&lt;/p&gt;</description>
